About.paragraph: As a software engineer, my goal is to write clean programs that are easy to maintain. I enjoy the creative and critical thinking that it takes to design efficient software, and I use my downtime to sharpen my skills and master new technologies. My best work happens in a collaborative environment where a growth-mindset is at the center of every project.
